{
  "stem": "18470.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were all absorbed in trying to stay alive physically, on the one hand, to fulfill our-- our objective goals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rabbinic Jewish scholarship always was something I was interested in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So was law and teaching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as happens with impressionable people, the last greatest teacher you had is the field that you want to go into.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One man was a brilliant historian of the Chinese experience, Professor Levy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was at Brooklyn College, and that was excellent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I graduated Brooklyn College in 1952.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took nine months, and went to Europe and Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was involuntary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I again went with this childhood friend of mine, Stanley Edwop, and we went to Montreal to catch a ship, a student ship that took us to Europe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were going to go to Zeebrugge, Belgium, and from there to Paris, and Paris down to the Riviera, and from the Riviera to get on a boat at Genoa, to go to Palestine, then Israel.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] got on this boat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it hit a ship, somewhere near Zeebrugge, sprung a huge leak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was towed into the Bremerhaven harbor-- and-- where it was to be fixed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there we got a compensation ticket to go to Paris, which would have been the ultimate stop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the train went through Oberwesel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is where I had this great anxiety attack, as to whether or not to get off the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the train landed, stopped at Oberwesel, Stanley and I grabbed our rucksacks, and we got off the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember being terribly excited, and not in a positive sense, just agitated, and wondered about what we should do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my feet started to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
